eland, H.J., Robert, M., Persistently declining oxygen levels in the interior waters of the eastern subarctic Pacific (2007) Prog. Oceanogr., 75, pp. 179-199; Wong, C.S., Waser, N.A.D., Nojiri, Y., Whitney, F.A., Page, J.S., Zeng, J., Seasonal cycles of nutrients and dissolved inorganic carbon at high and mid latitudes in the North Pacific Ocean during the Skaugran cruises: Determination of new production and nutrient uptake ratios (2002) Deep-Sea Res., Part 2, Top. Stud. Oceanogr., 49, pp. 5317-5338; Yang, M.-S., Nelson, M.W., Food habits of the Commercially Important Groundfishes in the Gulf of Alaska in 1990, 1993, and 1996 (2000) NOAA Tech. Memo., AFSC112, 174p","Ono, T.; Subarctic Fisheries Oceanography Division, Hokkaido National Fisheries Research Institute, Kushiro, Japan; email: tono@fra.affrc.go.jp",,,,,,,,08866236,,,,"English","Global Biogeochem. Cycles",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-65549117263
